flowchart TD
    Start([Pop URL from frontier]) --> P{Politeness gate}
    P --> F[HTTP fetch]
    F --> R{Status?}
    R -->|429 / 503| Backoff[Adaptive backoff] --> F
    R -->|2xx| CT{Content-type HTML?}
    R -->|4xx permanent| Fail[Mark failed]
    CT -->|no| Skip[Mark skipped]
    CT -->|yes| MR{Meta refresh?}
    MR -->|yes| Enq[Enqueue target same depth] --> Done
    MR -->|no| AB{Anti-bot signal?}
    AB -->|yes| KS[Kill-switch counter]
    AB -->|no| EX[Extract content]
    EX --> BT{Bot trap?}
    BT -->|yes| Fail
    BT -->|no| CV[Convert to MD with placeholders]
    CV --> W[Write note + sidecar]
    W --> LD[Discover links from raw HTML]
    LD --> Done([Mark done])
